dcterms:description: The MICCAI 2015 head and neck (HaN) organ-at-risk (OAR) segmentation challenge dataset contains a training set of 33 CT images and a test set of 15 CT images, with manually labeled organ segmentation masks for 9 organs.
dcterms:title: MICCAI 2015 head and neck (HaN) organ-at-risk (OAR) segmentation challenge dataset

dcterms:description: The in-house abdomen multi-organ segmentation dataset (ABD-110) contains 110 contrast-enhanced CT images and 11 organs, manually delineated by an experienced doctor.
dcterms:title: In-house abdomen multi-organ segmentation dataset (ABD-110)
